The Most Commonly Asked “How” Questions On Google

What are the most popular “How” questions on Google? How much are digital marketers willing to pay for these “How” terms? Did this thought even cross your mind for even a second. Well, worry not. The data provided here will surely serve as a goldmine for these digital marketers. Let’s take a look.

Well, the entire list of top 1000 most frequently asked “How” questions on Google is given below for your reference.  Alongside you will also find the global search volume and cost-per-click (CPC) data. CPC or cost-per-click refers to the amount advertisers pay to advertise for that term on Google.

WHAT are the most popular “How” QUESTIONs IN THE WORLD?

Now this is interesting. Taking a close look at the results, we were shocked to find out that the most searched “How” question on Google was – How to register to vote. A little over 1 million people search for this term every month! Coming in a close second was the question – How to be single with a similar number of searches. The third “How” question in Google was How I met your mother.

Like this, there are many more shocking results or rather questions that show up in this list of the most asked “How” questions on Google.

The values under the ‘Global Search Volume’ column are monthly averages calculated using the data collected over the last 6 months. The entire list of “Do” keywords has been generated using Mondovo’s Free Keyword Research Tool in just a few clicks and within seconds.
